      Subclasses of Interpolator in org.anchoranalysis.image.voxel.interpolator 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  InterpolatorImgLib2
      Performs interpolation using ImgLib2.
      class  InterpolatorImgLib2Lanczos
      An interpolator that uses Lanczos resampling as implemented in Imglib2.
      class  InterpolatorImgLib2Linear
      An interpolator that uses linear interpolation as implemented in Imglib2.
      class  InterpolatorImgLib2NearestNeighbor
      An interpolator that uses nearest neighbor interpolation as implemented in Imglib2.
      class  InterpolatorNone
      Doesn't do any interpolation, just copies a single value for each voxel.
      class  InterpolatorRecordExecutionTime
      Calls another Interpolator recording each interpolation call via a ExecutionTimeRecorder.
      Methods in org.anchoranalysis.image.voxel.interpolator that return Interpolator 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Interpolator InterpolatorFactory.binaryResizing(int outOfBoundsValue)
      An Interpolator that is suitable for resizing a binary raster-image, restricted to two possible intensity values only.
      Interpolator InterpolatorFactory.noInterpolation()
      An Interpolator that is effectively disabled, and performs no interpolation, copying a single (minimal corner) value for each voxel.
      Interpolator InterpolatorFactory.rasterResizing()
      An Interpolator that is suitable for resizing a raster-image with a range of intensity values.
